Sea365.SeaRobotDesc: seaROBOT is an automation marketing robot. It is a marketing software that automatically sends messages to the ships coming to the destination ports and communicates with the ships' captains.
Sea365.SeaRobotDetail: seaROBOT is an automation marketing robot. It is a marketing software that automatically sends messages to the ships coming to the destination ports and communicates with the ships' captains. Automatically scans the specified ports and finds the ships. Automatically sends message to the ships identified during the scan. Using the parameters such as flag, ship type, tonnage, helps you to easily find the vessel you are looking for. Offers the posibility of sending mail and telex to the ship.
Sea365.SeaSatDesc: Avs Marine Technologies specializes in supplying and delivering highly reliable mobile and ﬁxed satellite communications solutions to businesses, public institutions and consumers all over the world. Through satellite connectivity, AVS Marine Technologies oﬀers, fast, secure and eﬀicient telecommunications all over the world, even in the most remote locations and tailored to face extreme conditions. We bring telecommunication systems where existing cellular or terrestrial networks are unreliable or non-existing and provide the only available technology with truly global capabilities.
Sea365.SeaSatDetail: Avs Marine Technologies specializes in supplying and delivering highly reliable mobile and ﬁxed satellite communications solutions to businesses, public institutions and consumers all over the world. Through satellite connectivity, AVS Marine Technologies oﬀers, fast, secure and eﬀicient telecommunications all over the world, even in the most remote locations and tailored to face extreme conditions. We bring telecommunication systems where existing cellular or terrestrial networks are unreliable or non-existing and provide the only available technology with truly global capabilities.seaSAT is a service that provides data and voice service over the satellite. Provides seamless data and voice services wherever the ship is found in the world. Thanks to its various types of service options, provides the supply of satellite terminals suitable for the shipowner budget and the use packages appropriate to these terminals. Facilitates the communication between the ship and the office and enables the ship's crew to comunicate with their families - their loved ones in the most effective way.
Sea365.SeaSupplyDesc: seaSUPPLY is a software for performing purchasing and selling transactions of technical, consumables and provision.
Sea365.SeaSupplyDetail: seaSUPPLY is a software for performing purchasing and selling transactions of technical, consumables and provision.The program is able to carry out transactions such as purchasing, price comparison, sales and post-delivery invoice and the preparation for delivery of invoices by comparing the invoice with delivery documents.At the end of the operations, it follows-up the stocks of ships and, in connection with it, sets up the reports of the ship budget followings.Sea Supply also provides an evaluation follow-up of the feedback of our operations, customers and managers in order to monitor the service quality of contracted suppliers.
Sea365.SeaSupportDesc: The AVS Marine Technologies team can provide IT support to maritime companies and ships on through phone calls 24/7 or on-site operation.
Sea365.SeaSupportDetail: The AVS Marine Technologies team can provide IT support to maritime companies and ships on through phone calls 24/7 or on-site operation. Server installation and management Network installation and management Virtualization Supply of IT products and parts Licensing
Sea365.Sim4CrewDetail: AVS provides seamen with Sim 4 Crew sim cards, so they can seamlessly communicate via phone and internet anywhere in the world.Sim 4 Crew has everything seamen would need in a powerful sim card for calls, SMS, and data.Features of Sim 4 Crew are: Global Roaming Amazing Prices Online Top-up Sales Network No Expiry Date24/7 Assistance

Sea365.Welcome: The relationships we have established with suppliers, distributors and manufacturers have helped us create a powerful network based on trust and mutual benefit.The advantages of working with AVS: A strong network Impeccable purchasing power The capacity to reach anywhere through one single contact point Cost-effective solutions for ship owners and ship managers
SeaHubDetail: seaHUB is a management program for ship management companies and shipowners to manage their ships.Plans and monitors the operations on board.Provides easy access to records and documents related to all the operations performed on board.Ensures regular monitoring of ship inventories. Organizes purchases and provides their viewing in an easy manner.Makes the ship's instant running cost calculation.Creates and archive the ISM documents.Provides keeping of bunker records in voyages.Creates and archive safety (Inspection, audit, control) records.Records and keeps track of work/rest hours, accounting data and all the documents related to the crew.Provides file and data transmission on Internet.Features of seaHUB: It is the first Turkish software to have international certificates. It has 16 different modules and the 17th module is currently under development. More than 150 vessels have been using it for 9 years.All modules are well-integrated.Runs on a low usage of WIFI.Also works offline.Users have 24/7 support.Supports multi-user.Easy to use interface.
